reviewText: only for not the faint of heart. 5 star for some

Great show.  It is one of those that is so addictive I can not wait to watch another episode, then comes the wait for next season, there in is the benefit of  these season-sets, you can get the past seasons and watch them while you wait for next season to release.  I love having the discs to rewatch and share with family and friends after I am through.  Shipped fast (2 days) and well packaged.
Great gift for the Yukon Men lover, great quality
I have enjoyed this series very much and have viewed it more than once.
It's a great show. It's about a small village in Alaska. The people there live a subsistence life style and it shows what they do every day to survive up there. Very interesting.

we live in Alaska and love Alaska shows. Some of these type of programs are very dramatized and this show isn't as much.
